      %label.choice{:for => 'Vehicle'} Have a vehicle and/or trailer to lend for bike pickups/scrap days
      %div
      = check_box_tag(:Grant, true, params[:Grant], :class => 'checkbox')
      %label.choice{:for => 'Grant'} Grant Writing/Grant finding/Fundraising
